Blog Post App

Models.
1 - Blog - Title, Description , Image , Category, Author(blog), comments, likes/fav
2 - User - name, picture, contact/email, followers, following , blogs.
3 - Book - name, Description , Image, Category, Author(book), Comments, likes/fav,

Routes.
1 - Blog
- /api/blogs
- /api/myBlogs
- /api/blogs/:id
- /api/blogs/addBlog
- /api/blogs/updateBlog
- /api/blogs/deleteBlog

2 - User
- /api/register
- /api/login
- api/myProfile
- /api/users
- /api/users/:id
- /api/users/update
- api/users/follow/:id

3 - Book
- /api/books
- api/myBooks
- /api/books/:id
- /api/books/addBook
- /api/books/deleteBook


Features.

- Login/Sign Up(Add User)
- Create Articles/Blogs
- View All Blogs
- Update Author
- Edit own profile
- Edit/Delete own blog
- fav/like Users (Blogger)
- Follow other Users (Blogger)
- comment articles/blogs.
- Create Book
- Delete Book
- View Own Books
- View all books
- Comments/Reviews on books

Todos.

- Change the database from mongoDB to mySQL.
- Authirization of All endpoints.
